// PropertiesPane (diagram)
// Right-side panel for SMACH diagram editing.
// Always shows an "Add State" button. When a node is selected, additionally
// shows "Add Transition" and property editor fields (name, description).
// Resets form fields when selected node changes.

FUNCTION PropertiesPane(selectedNodeId, onAddState, onAddTransition, onEditProperties) -> JSX  EXPORT
  Manages local properties state {name, description}.
  Resets properties to empty strings when selectedNodeId changes.
  IF selectedNodeId: shows selected node ID, Add Transition button, and
  property inputs. ELSE shows "No state selected" placeholder.

---

FUNCTION handlePropertyChange(key, value) -> void
  Updates local properties state. Calls onEditProperties(selectedNodeId, updatedProps).
